docs.snippet: Scenes enacted last week at the massive gates of the Bank of France at 1 Rue de la Vrilliere, Paris, when long queues of citizens waited to push franc notes through the wickets for bars of gold, were reminiscent of the dark days here in March, 1933,...
docs.lead_paragraph: Scenes enacted last week at the massive gates of the Bank of France at 1 Rue de la Vrilliere, Paris, when long queues of citizens waited to push franc notes through the wickets for bars of gold, were reminiscent of the dark days here in March, 1933, when our own Old Lady of Liberty Street was besieged by those clamoring for gold coin.

docs.snippet: BUENOS AIRES, June 3. -- The Chaco peace negotiations are on the verge of a complete breakdown. There was little prospect tonight that they could be held together even long enough to permit inauguration of the much-hoped-for direct negotiations...
docs.lead_paragraph: BUENOS AIRES, June 3. -- The Chaco peace negotiations are on the verge of a complete breakdown. There was little prospect tonight that they could be held together even long enough to permit inauguration of the much-hoped-for direct negotiations between the Bolivian and Paraguayan Foreign Ministers.

headline.main: CHACO PEACE TALKS ARE NEAR COLLAPSE; Bolivia Rejects Proposal for Demobilizing Before Direct Negotiations Start.
